ESP Web Tools
Version: 10.3.0
Upstream: https://github.com/esphome/esp-web-tools
Source of these files: https://unpkg.com/esp-web-tools@10.3.0/dist/web/
License: Apache License 2.0

These files are the upstream `dist/web/` browser build, vendored unmodified
(apart from a one-time license header comment prepended to install-button.js)
and served from Pantry Raider's own origin. The Web Serial flasher on the
Bandit Cubs page must run with no external network requests, so the whole
code-split bundle is co-located here; install-button.js dynamically imports
the sibling chunks by their relative (./) paths.

